Academic citation note: The content of the `case-method/` skill (SKILL.md and
references/*.md) is a synthesis of published academic literature. When citing
specific methodological arguments in your own work, please cite the original
authors (e.g., Sartori 1970, King/Keohane/Verba 1994, George & Bennett 2005)
rather than this skill. A complete bibliography is provided in
`case-method/references/07_术语表与学者争论.md` section 7.3.
